## Naming Conventions
- Folders: `kebab-case`
- Topic files: `kebab-case.md`
- Journal entries: `DD.md` (one file per day) inside `YYYY/MM/` folders
- Code examples: named by language convention (`.ts`, `.py`, `.go`, etc.)

## Restrictions
- Do NOT search the web. Only use existing workspace files and training knowledge.
- Prioritize notes already created in the knowledge base over external sources.
- When answering questions about a book/topic, check if notes exist in the domain folders first.

## Response Guidelines
- All content must be written in English only
- Follow the standard response format: Overview → Details → Attention Points → Examples → Diagram → Summary
